---
By: Vimala Thakar
Locus:
  Page: 275
  Verse: 7
Tags:
  - Journey
---
To take a journey of a thousand miles, you have to begin with the first
step from the place where you stand; the romantic description of the
journey and the things the body sees on the way and the description of the
scenery are of no use unless you lift your foot and take the first step.
